my.apps.onboarding.modal.screen2.text:
Curious to learn more about an app? Hover over its icon and click the menu that appears, then select "Learn more about the app".

This menu also gives you direct access to Library resources by clicking "View examples". Perfect for inspiration!

Is there a new feature you shouldn't miss in an app?
A red dot will appear on the "bell" icon at the top right, opening an info panel.
